}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== The device may be the same as the WS-WN511N1.
"XDX-RN502 V2.0" is silkscreened on the board.
The manufacturer of this device appears to be [http://sztianhao.com Shenzhen Century Xinyang Technology Co., Ltd (widemac)].
The included power adapter may be an '''unbranded''' FJ-SW0502000U (5V, 2000mA). ID/OD/Len measurements are approximate.
